    <description>&lt;DIV&gt;As can see from the previous post many things were promised and not implemented for some reason or another.&amp;nbsp; instead of fixxing some they just removed them completely.&amp;nbsp; That 50% melee hitbox is a joke.&amp;nbsp; Imagine getting hit from someone 10 steps behind you while trying to get room to get a spell off that takes 4-5 seconds to cast.&amp;nbsp; Dispell was never adressed other than AHR bracer which they just changed to not work in pvp at all.&amp;nbsp; PvP gear has remained the same as when points first came out and soon pvp points became totaly meaningless.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Also, a new change that was put into play recently, looting all your corpse with out it being rezed causes the corpse to remain.&amp;nbsp; That corpse used to be looted after a PvP death making it so the dead player had to run back.&amp;nbsp; Now the corpses cant be looted and the corpse remains.&amp;nbsp; With people going to shadow rest with gear on all it takes is a rez for them to be back fighting again.&amp;nbsp; They are rezed back in fully dressed and if a druid or shaman rezes then fully buffed as well.&amp;nbsp; That is bull.&amp;nbsp; They should have to sit out for the rez effects to wear off.&amp;nbsp; A melee freshly rezed doesnt even have to wait to (med) they can engage in the fight immedatly.&amp;nbsp; There should be no corpse if you are PKed.&amp;nbsp; Or it should be able to be looted again.&amp;nbsp; They dont lose experience for them to worry about.&amp;nbsp; The penalty is only that they have to wait for the PvP death effects to wear off.&amp;nbsp; The last few guild battles noone won becuase everyone was just getting rezed in the second they died, healed conviction tossed on them and haste.&amp;nbsp; Then they were ready to go again.&amp;nbsp; Total time out of the fight is maybe 2 minutes.&amp;nbsp; You should not have to kill the same person 3-4 times in a 20 minute time span.&amp;nbsp; There needs to be stricter consquences for a pvp death then losing some points that dont matter, your buffs, and 2 minutes of zoning.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
