    <item>
      <title>Fix PvP</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=PVP&amp;message.id=11404#M11404</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;I do not know where to post this and if someone does and can either link this thread or copy this to the correct place I would be greatful.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;To start off with, I am the second best geared necromancer on Zek.&amp;nbsp; I have played on sullon zek and then zek for the last 5 years.&amp;nbsp; In the past the developers have felt the need to change melee damage, hit rate, spell damage, max spell damage and resists.&amp;nbsp; Some of these were needed and helped PvP for that time in the progression of guilds.&amp;nbsp; It is now time to relook and change these again.&amp;nbsp; When melee damage was upgraded it was for weapons that had a max damage of 45.&amp;nbsp; Now there are tons of people running around with 90+ damage weapons.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;On my necromancer i am 9500 hps unbuffed, have all defensive aas, 100 avoidance, max stun resists, dodge 3, and high AC for a caster of 1500ish.&amp;nbsp; Yet in PvP I am chain stunned by any melee class who can hit for 1,000 to 4,500.&amp;nbsp; Melee range was modified so that can hot from much further away as well.&amp;nbsp; Now as a dps class I have 1 spell that lands and it lands maybe 2 out of 5 times.&amp;nbsp; That is our ancient tap spell from OoW era.&amp;nbsp; When it does land it crits for an amazing amount of 30.&amp;nbsp; That is correct 300 damage and if im lucky i can get a crit heal on top for 600 heal to myself.&amp;nbsp; Now I know what you are thinking I am a necromancer and should do DoTs as well, but none land.&amp;nbsp; If you are lucky you can get a level 65 heal over time leech called Night's Beacon to land, but that is dispellable and does 200 damage per tick to people who have dot shielding and 13000 hps.&amp;nbsp; So there we have a dps class who cant do any dps in PvP.&amp;nbsp; I am getting tired of it.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;My guild 6 months ago had 12 active necromancers.&amp;nbsp; Now all but 2 have quit due to our class being broken in pvp.&amp;nbsp; In a recent Guild&amp;nbsp; vrse Guild pvp battle the most killed class was necromancer.&amp;nbsp; One necro from my guild and one in the other were killed about 8 times each in 4 hours.&amp;nbsp; The most any other class had was 2 deaths.&amp;nbsp; The combined necromancer kills were 5.&amp;nbsp; One melee alone had 22.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Necromancers are not a healing class, we are not a support class, we are not a defensive class, we are a DAMAGING class.&amp;nbsp; Yet we have no ability to do any.&amp;nbsp; We are sitting ducks.&amp;nbsp; Other casters classes are in the same boat as necromancers, but I cant comment on them as I have no first hand knowledge.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I know sony does not care about the only PvP server, but they need to take some time and balance pvp again.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Here are some things that need to be changed:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Make other spells other than magic ones pvp options for necromancers.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Have melee who hit for 4,500 be able to get hit for the same amount.&amp;nbsp; It is not fair for a class like a warrior to 1 round someone when our spells are limited to 40% of thier hps.&amp;nbsp; That should only be for the spells it was intended for: Manaburn, lifeburn, and HT.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Change Melee stuns so they no longer are irresistable.&amp;nbsp; Any monk with a Tstaff even in bazaar gear can keep any other&amp;nbsp;class chain stunned.&amp;nbsp; In a monk duel i watched this week the first one to click 2.0 was the winner becuase the other was just stunned for the rest of the fight.&amp;nbsp; The whole fight lasted 20 seconds.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Potions should be removed on Zek.&amp;nbsp; I will spend almost all my mana fighting someone only to have all the damage i just did healed by 1 potion.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Melee damage needs to be reduced for pvp.&amp;nbsp; for example a sk can hit for 1500 , rogues can backstab from any angle for 3000 and get tripples if behind, warriors can hit for 4,500, zerkers hit for 4,000, monks hit for 2,000, pallys fir 2,000, rangers can hot for 1000 with a one hander and more with thier bow and the new DohD spell HoA, and bards hit for 750 with one handers.&amp;nbsp; Everyone should see how fast a 9500 caster lasts while taking 2000 average per swing hits.&amp;nbsp; I have been 1 rounded fully raid buffed.&amp;nbsp; Fix it so casters have some chance against this.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Pet hits need to be upgraded.&amp;nbsp; They were lowered, but that needs to be relooked at.&amp;nbsp; With my anguish focus my pet hits in pvp for 12 per hit.&amp;nbsp; Only thing he is useful for is maybe a stun, but AAs have stopped that now.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I know this whole post seems like I am crying becuase I have been killed a lot, but that is not it.&amp;nbsp; I just want to have a competitive chance.&amp;nbsp; If others have any other good suggestions on how to fix pvp please list them below.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Hangman Gallows&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;70 Necromancer&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Officer of Hate&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
